<HEADLINE> Bangladesh, Japan Sign Accord on Grant Aid for Debt Relief </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, June 22 (Xinhua) -- Bangladesh and Japan Tuesday signed
an agreement on Japanese grant aid for the former's debt relief
amounting to 105.24 million U.S. dollars, the national news agency
BSS reported.
</P>
<P>
