<HEADLINE> ADB Approves Education Loan to Bangladesh </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, June 22 (Xinhua) -- The Asian Development Bank (ADB)
approved Tuesday a 60-million-U.S.-dollar loan for Bangladesh to
implement its secondary education development plan during the next
decade.
</P>
<P>
