foundation for a systemic reform of the country's secondary
education, including policy and institutional reforms and capacity
building, ADB said in a news release.
</P>
<P>
The loan will be repayable over 32 years with a grace period of
eight years. It carries an interest charge of 1 percent per annum
during the grace period and 1.5 percent thereafter. 
